  "body": "Since we now have `Stateless function components` it would be convenient to transition to statefull ones with minimal changes:\n\n``` js\n// before\nvar Aquarium = (props) => {\n  var fish = getFish(props.species);\n  return <Tank>{fish}</Tank>;\n};\n```\n\n``` js\n// after\nclass Aquarium extends React.Component {\n  render (props, state) {\n    var fish = getFish(props.species);\n    return <Tank>{fish}</Tank>;\n  }\n}\n```\n",
